Downloading the VM Image
------------------------
In order to keep the PF_RING distribution reasonably small, we have uploaded
the VM image on sourceforge at http://sourceforge.net/projects/ntop/files/PF_RING/vPF_RING/

Please unzip VM images prior to use them.


Utility Scripts
---------------
This directory contains some utility scripts:

- if-up.sh
  Utility script used by start-vm.sh (see below).

- load-kvm.sh
  Load kernel modules and setup bridge interfaces. Please execute this
  script *before* starting any QEMU VM.  

- start-vm.sh
  Example script for loading a VM with network connectivity.